<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.1">
<l>coṉṉāl virōtami tākiluñ colluvaṉ kēṇmiṉō</l>
<l>veṉṉāvi liṉkavi yāṉoru varkkuṅ koṭukkilēṉ</l>
<l>ṟeṉṉā teṉāveṉ ṟuvaṇṭu muraṟiru vēṅkaṭat</l>
<l>teṉṉāṉai yeṉṉappa ṉemperu māṉuḷa ṉākavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I speak, even though it is controversial, I shall speak. Listen:</l>
<l>I cannot give the sweet poem on my tongue to anybody</l>
<l>– that in sacred Vēṅkaṭam where bees hum “sssss”</l>
<l>he is my elephant, my father, my great lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
